description: The Southwest is getting something great today, courtesy of the one and only Kool Twists.Top quality soft serve ice cream and icy cold beverages are always a welcome treat under the Arizona sun, and nobody serves them up better than these fine folks. Cones, sundaes, milkshakes, and malts are just some of the things that your sweet tooth can look forward to when Kool Twists is on the scene.Don't miss the taste that's the talk of Tucson today!
name: Kool Twists
